WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
narrator: a guided tour of the headscale CLI surface.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:15.000
narrator: users — the namespace that owns nodes and keys.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:25.000
narrator: preauthkeys — single-use or reusable, scoped to a user.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:35.000
narrator: nodes — every machine that has run tailscale up.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:45.000
narrator: routes — subnets advertised by a peer for split-tunnel reach.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:55.000
narrator: policy — the HUJSON ACL document, set and gotten via CLI.

00:00:55.000 --> 00:01:05.000
narrator: api-keys — long-lived tokens for ops automation.

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:15.000
narrator: every command mirrors the upstream headscale shape 1-for-1.

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:25.000
narrator: existing tailscale-ops runbooks transfer with zero rewrites.
